Package: timechunks
Title: Named Time Periods for Academic, Fiscal, and Custom Calendars
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("First", "Last", email = "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a vector type for named time periods that cross calendar
    year boundaries, such as academic semesters, fiscal quarters, and custom
    period systems. Supports multiple input formats, chronological sorting,
    and full tidyverse compatibility via the vctrs package.
